@startuml
title Current Booking Process — As-Is

actor "Guest" as guest
participant "Hotel Website" as website
participant "Booking Partner" as partner
participant "Booking Agency" as agency
participant "Channel Manager" as cm
participant "Hotel Support Agent" as agent
participant "ERP System" as erp

note over website, erp
  Assumption: Hotel Website has a direct API connection to the ERP system.
  Booking data is submitted automatically without manual intervention.
end note

note over partner, cm
  Assumption: Booking Partners integrate via the Channel Manager API.
  Booking and availability data is synced automatically to the ERP.
end note

== Path 1: Website Booking ==
guest -> website: Books room
website -> erp: Sends booking via API

== Path 2: Booking Partner ==
guest -> partner: Books room
partner -> cm: Sends booking via API
cm -> erp: Syncs booking automatically

== Path 3: Booking Agency ==
guest -> agency: Requests booking
agency -> agent: Sends booking confirmation via email
agent -> erp: Manually enters booking data

@enduml
